  <brief_title>Rollover Study Protocol for Pediatric Patients in South Africa for Continued Access to Emtricitabine</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Rollover Protocol to Provide Subjects Completing the FTC-203 Study in South Africa With Continued Access to Emtricitabine</official_title>
