  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objectives of this trial are to provide FTC-203 study participants in South
      Africa with continued access to the study drug, emtricitabine (FTC), following completion of
      the FTC-203 study and to collect long-term safety information in participants receiving
      emtricitabine in combination with other antiretroviral agents.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
